cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.GR, cs.LG, cs.AI. 

The paper deals with image processing and computer vision, specifically single image reflection removal. Therefore, cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is the most likely category. The paper also involves physically based rendering, which falls under cs.GR (Graphics) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the proposed network structure involves deep learning, which is a subfield of cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence).
